<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Course Under Review Notification</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f8ff; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; padding: 20px; } .container { background: #fff;
      padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); } h1 { color: #337ab7; border-bottom: 2px solid #337ab7;
      padding-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h1>Course Under Review</h1>
      <p>Dear {{{firstname}}} {{{lastname}}},</p>
      <p>We wanted to let you know that your course submission titled "{{{title}}}" is currently <strong>under review</strong>.</p>
      <p>Our team is carefully evaluating your course to ensure it meets our quality standards. We will notify you once we have made a decision.</p>
      <p>Thank you for your patience and for choosing to share your knowledge with us.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />
        The Neargami Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>